content:
I have a dataset of sports and their equipment. The dataset is in the form of a JSON file as shown below:
{
  "sports": [
    {
      "name": "tennis",
      "equipment": ["racquet", "ball"]
    },
    {
      "name": "badminton",
      "equipment": ["racquet", "shuttlecock"]
    },
    {
      "name": "squash",
      "equipment": ["racquet", "ball"]
    }
  ]
}
Based on this dataset, can you name two sports that use a racquet? Please provide the names of the sports.
